Our simple configuration looks like:

```
// relay.config.js
module.exports = {
  src: './src',
  schema: './schema.graphql',
  language: 'javascript',
  exclude: ['**/node_modules/**', '**/__mocks__/**', '**/__generated__/**'],
};
```
